Quickstrike:





Quickstrike chuckled shortly along with Dark Mouse. "Well, ah ain't 
gonna hold on t' ya all day." He picked her up, with one hand 
supporting her back and the other supporting her legs. He put her on 
the bunk.

"Ah'm gonna see what Black Arachnia needs." He walked to the 
threshold of the doorway. "Ya want this opened or closed?"
